hopobject.body:
VisualGDB is a Visual Studio add-in that allows developing and debugging projects for many Linux-based devices including Beaglebone.

For more details see the following tutorials:

  • VisualGDB Beaglebone tutorial
  • VisualGDB Beaglebone Cross-Compiler tutorial
